<div class="container">
	<h2>Icon Alignment Adjustment</h2>
	<h6 class="m-b-1">Horizontal Alignment (.icon-adjust-horiz)</h6>
	<p><span class="ico-lab"></span> This icon is how it normally appears.</p>
	<p><span class="ico-lab icon-adjust-horiz"></span> This icon is adjusted remove extra horizontal space.</p>
	<p>Any <code>-arrow-right</code> icons have extra margin on left instead of <span class="text-nowrap">right. <a href="#0"><span class="ico-double-arrow-right-sm icon-adjust-horiz"></span></a></span></p>
	<h6 class="m-b-1">Vertical Alignment (.icon-adjust-vert)</h6>
	<p class="micro m-b-0"><span class="ico-calendar-sm"></span> These icons have not been vertically adjusted.</p>
	<p class="micro m-b-0"><span class="ico-map-marker-sm"></span> This impacts the line-height of each paragraph.</p>
	<p class="micro"><span class="ico-person-sm"></span> Which you can see when multiple paragraphs stack.</p>
	<p class="micro m-b-0"><span class="ico-calendar-sm icon-adjust-vert"></span> These icons have been vertically adjusted.</p>
	<p class="micro m-b-0"><span class="ico-map-marker-sm icon-adjust-vert"></span> The icon no longer impacts the line-height of each paragraph.</p>
	<p class="micro"><span class="ico-person-sm icon-adjust-vert"></span> Which you can see when multiple paragraphs stack.</p>
</div>
